Name: Fuel Economy
Description: This compound value type to represents estimates for fuel economy for a vehicle based on laboratory tests conducted by manufacturers according to federal regulations.

Properties.Name: City MPG
Properties.Description: The fuel economy of the model year driving in the city

Properties.Name: Highway MPG
Properties.Description: The fuel economy of the model year driving on the highway

Properties.Name: The combined fuel consumption of the vehicle
The authority reporting the fuel economy values. Could be the manufacturer, an official testing facility, etc.
